{"tid":1218210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到好多曱甴爬上身 (有片慎入)","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:14:50.000Z","uid":260451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e41d0ca6aba1aaa96dd5bcfd215515bec156568","tid":1218210,"uid":260451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的,話說尋晚發夢就去左花園街度行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行下就見到有間鋪頭就放左好多曱甴係度,即刻起曬雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然間,個鋪頭伙記拎起一箱曱甴行出去,一個唔小心扑街就成箱曱甴倒落個途人度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲反應係點就唔洗講啦(我相信啲狗都係會即刻理智斷線),有啲爬左入衫,有啲爬入鞋,真係諗起都唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n各位如果拎住好多曱甴真係要小心啲,一爬上身真係捉到捉唔住(特別係著住裝甲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3SS1akWXWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE3SS1akWXWk&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=6e50f90b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3SS1akWXWk</a>"}]}